briefdescription.para: GNU Radio logging wrapper for log4cpp library (C++ port of log4j)
Function to call configuration macro from python. Note: Configuration is only updated if filename or watch_period has changed.

parameterdescription.para: Seconds to wait between checking for changes in conf file. Watch_period defaults to 0 in which case the file is not watched for changes

briefdescription.para: Function to return logger names to python.
Function to reset logger configuration from python.
